reviewText:
This is a concert of praise within Eastside Baptist Church in Marietta, GA. Babbie sings live with a 120 voice mass choir.
Here are the tracks: 1) All In Favor 2) All Rise 3) Carry On 4) Each One, Reach One 5) God Has Another Plan 6) God Thank You 7) Great Is Thy Faithfullness 8) Hallowed Be Thy Name 9) He'll Find A Way 10) Keep the Rocks Silent 11) The Peace of the Lord 12) Somebody Ought To Tell 13) With All My Heart 14) You're the One
